unmatchedTraits.name: Always Vigilant
unmatchedTraits.description:
You can't let anything get by you; not anymore. I'm always watching for the 
next disaster.

unmatchedTraits.name:
Cooked for the Squad 

*(Red Talon Contractors only)*
unmatchedTraits.description:
Red Talon doesn't have a lot of full-time cooks, but when you're good, you 
get the job.

unmatchedTraits.name:
Facilities Engineer 

*(Red Talon Contractors only)*
unmatchedTraits.description:
You want to live somewhere long-term, you're going to need an 
infrastructure.

unmatchedTraits.name: Filthy
unmatchedTraits.description:
In the nineteenth century, people only bathed like once a year. This is 
frontier life, man.

unmatchedTraits.name:
Firearms Enthusiast 

*(Red Talon Contractors only)*
unmatchedTraits.description:
Your weapon is the only thing between you and certain death. You have to 
take care of it.

unmatchedTraits.name: Flatuent
unmatchedTraits.description: He who smelt it dealt it.

unmatchedTraits.name:
Front Line Experience 

*(Red Talon Contractors only)*
unmatchedTraits.description: I've been on the real frontier. It's a constant siege, day in and day out.

unmatchedTraits.name: Goes by Last Name
unmatchedTraits.description:
My friends always called me by my last name, and it sort of stuck 
throughout my life.

unmatchedTraits.name: Hated Camping
unmatchedTraits.description:
My idea of camping is a hotel without room service. Sleeping on the ground 
is not an option.

unmatchedTraits.name: Lacks Boundaries
unmatchedTraits.description:
You don't want a hug, or a backrub? How am I supposed to say hi, then? A 
pat on the butt?

unmatchedTraits.name: Learned Computing
unmatchedTraits.description:
I don't know if we'll ever have tech industry again, but I've been reading 
up on what's left.

unmatchedTraits.name: Learned Medicine
unmatchedTraits.description:
Now that death is around ever corner, I've started reading up on first aid 
and CPR.

unmatchedTraits.name: Learned to Cook
unmatchedTraits.description:
I've read a stack of cookbooks since the outbreak. I think I may just know 
what I'm doing.

unmatchedTraits.name: Learned to Garden
unmatchedTraits.description:
I read everything I could about gardening after the outbreak, hoping I 
could put it to use.

unmatchedTraits.name: Learned Utilities
unmatchedTraits.description:
I've been reading books on plumbing and electrical work, in case we ever 
need to fix something.

unmatchedTraits.name: Left for Dead
unmatchedTraits.description: *Unknown*

unmatchedTraits.name: Mentally Trained
unmatchedTraits.description:
I went through a training regimen that prepared me to handle a lot of 
different mental tasks.

unmatchedTraits.name: No Filter
unmatchedTraits.description:
Folks think I say whatever pops into my head. Maybe I should pop something 
into THEIR heads.

unmatchedTraits.name: Noisy
unmatchedTraits.description: Yeah, I'm banging pots and pans. How else do you make breakfast?

unmatchedTraits.name: Physically Trained
unmatchedTraits.description:
I went through a training regimen that prepared me to handle a lot of 
different physical tasks.

unmatchedTraits.name:
Practices at the Range 

*(Red Talon Contractors only)*
unmatchedTraits.description: Being good isn't enough. You need a headshot every time.

unmatchedTraits.name: Short Change Hero
unmatchedTraits.description: This ain't no place for no Hero. This ain't no place for no better man.

unmatchedTraits.name: Talks Loudly
unmatchedTraits.description: My volume dial has two settings: Off and HEEEEEEY!

unmatchedTraits.name: Taxidermist
unmatchedTraits.description:
I thought of putting myself forward as a sort of surgeon â€¦ then I realized 
that was insane.

unmatchedTraits.name: Trained at Fighting
unmatchedTraits.description:
I went through a training regimen for a variety of different combat 
scenarios.

unmatchedTraits.name: Trained at Shooting
unmatchedTraits.description:
I went through a training regimen that taught me a variety of different 
shooting techniques.

unmatchedTraits.name:
Worked as a Pioneer 

*(Red Talon Contractors only)*
unmatchedTraits.description:
We were sent into newly cleared territory to build walls and prevent the 
zeds from coming back.
